time_range": "2025-06-16 16:10:02+00:00 to 2025-06-16 16:26:02+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "paymentservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["currencyservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于对日志数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了显著的异常调用链模式。以下是详细分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"FailedPrecondition\", \"Can't access cart storage\", \"Redis\", \"redis-cart:6379\", \"connection refused\", \"cartservice\", \"frontend\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis连接故障导致cartservice无法访问购物车存储，引发FailedPrecondition错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice日志显示'Can't access cart storage'和'Connecting to Redis: redis-cart:6379'，frontend服务出现FailedPrecondition错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice无法连接到redis-cart存储后端，导致连锁故障\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2实例出现158次FailedPrecondition错误，所有cartservice实例都有Redis连接尝试日志\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务因cartservice故障而出现大量请求错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有frontend实例(frontend-0/1/2)均出现'failed to add to cart: rpc error: code = FailedPrecondition desc = Can't access cart storage'错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n1. **明确的错误模式**：所有错误都围绕`FailedPrecondition`和`Can't access cart storage`，表明购物车存储访问问题\n\n2. **调用链异常**：\n   - frontend → cartservice → redis-cart 调用链中断\n   - cartservice无法连接到redis-cart:6379\n\n3. **故障范围**：\n   - 所有cartservice实例(cartservice-0/1/2)都出现连接问题\n   - 所有frontend实例都受到影响，出现大量购物车操作失败\n\n4. **关键证据**：cartservice日志明确显示正在尝试连接Redis数据库`redis-cart:6379`，但无法访问存储\n\n这表明redis-cart服务可能是根因，导致整个购物车功能链失效。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于Trace数据加载失败的情况，我将结合共识代理的分析结果和系统拓扑结构进行推理分析。根据共识代理的发现，我提供以下Trace专家的视角：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"cartservice->redis-cart\", \"frontend->cartservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice出现FailedPrecondition错误，无法访问购物车存储，连接Redis数据库redis-cart:6379时出现问题，这是调用链中最下游的异常点\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"作为redis-cart的直接调用方，因存储层连接失败而出现连锁故障，错误向上传播到前端服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有frontend实例的error_ratio从0.0飙升到0.66，表明前端服务因cartservice故障而大面积受影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Trace专家分析依据**：\n\n1. **调用链因果关系**：根据系统拓扑，`frontend → cartservice → redis-cart` 是明确的依赖路径，redis-cart作为最下游存储层，其故障会向上游传播。\n\n2. **根因定位原则**：在调用链中，最下游的异常通常是根因。redis-cart的连接失败直接导致cartservice无法正常工作。\n\n3. **错误传播模式**：从存储层(redis-cart)到业务层(cartservice)再到接入层(frontend)的错误传播路径清晰，符合典型的依赖故障传播模式。\n\n虽然Trace原始数据加载失败，但基于系统架构和共识代理的综合分析，redis-cart作为存储层故障是合理的根因推断。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于指标数据分析，我发现了多个关键异常模式。让我提供专业的指标分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有frontend实例的server_error_ratio和error_ratio均从0.0飙升到0.66-0.67，表明前端服务大面积故障\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: error_ratio从0.0到0.66；frontend-1: error_ratio从0.0到0.64；frontend-2: error_ratio从0.0到0.67\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice-0的error_ratio p99值从0.0飙升到23.4，显示严重错误率异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0的error_ratio p99变化率2.0，从0.0到23.4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice-2的error_ratio p99值从0.0飙升到51.82，显示严重错误率异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-2的error_ratio p99变化率2.0，从0.0到51.82\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"redis服务的error_ratio p99值从0.0飙升到2.39，显示Redis连接或响应异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0的error_ratio p99变化率2.0，从0.0到2.39\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0, checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkout服务实例的rrt_max显著增加，响应时间恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-0的rrt_max从175415到95951；checkoutservice-2的rrt_max从127860到71518.5\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n1. **前端服务全面故障**：所有frontend实例的error_ratio从0飙升到约0.66，这是最明显的故障现象\n\n2. **存储层异常证据**：\n   - `redis-cart-0`的error_ratio p99值异常（从0.0到2.39）\n   - `cartservice-0`的error_ratio p99值严重恶化（从0.0到23.4）\n\n3. **性能劣化**：\n   - checkoutservice响应时间显著增加（rrt_max大幅上升）\n   - 多个服务的rrt_max指标显示响应时间恶化\n\n**支持共识观点的关键证据**：指标数据确实显示redis-cart-0存在错误率异常，这与Log专家发现的\"Can't access cart storage\"错误高度一致。前端服务的大面积错误也验证了故障的连锁效应。"}
